 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"&gt;二、关于新农村新变化的题材。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"&gt;剧本要求：1、剧中人物为一男青年和一女青年，一位老奶奶，男的外出打工，因家里的老奶奶年纪大了需要人在身边照顾，于是决定回村，与分开一年的女友重逢，男的学到本领，两人决定一起创业的事，养殖种殖都可以，从重逢之后回到村里开始写。2、字数不少于一千，要求原创，未侵犯他人的著作权，如有侵犯他人著作权，由写作者承担所有法律责任，我方支付编写费用后，即拥有该作品的知识产权，有权对作品进行修改,组合和应用。&lt;/p&gt;KPPW2.2安装包默认数据均为测试演示数据，无任何商业意图，请各位站长测试后自行删除。如有违规，自行承责。\";s:9:\"task_file\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"task_pic\";N;s:8:\"indus_id\";s:2:\"16\";s:9:\"indus_pid\";s:1:\"3\";s:3:\"uid\";s:1:\"2\";s:8:\"username\";s:6:\"猪八戒\";s:10:\"start_time\";s:10:\"1365499846\";s:8:\"sub_time\";s:10:\"1365672646\";s:8:\"end_time\";s:10:\"1365759046\";s:11:\"sp_end_time\";N;s:4:\"city\";N;s:9:\"task_cash\";s:6:\"100.00\";s:9:\"real_cash\";s:5:\"90.00\";s:18:\"task_cash_coverage\";N;s:9:\"cash_cost\";s:6:\"100.00\";s:11:\"credit_cost\";s:4:\"0.00\";s:8:\"view_num\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"work_num\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"leave_num\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"focus_num\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"mark_num\";s:1:\"0\";s:11:\"is_delineas\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"kf_uid\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"pay_item\";N;s:8:\"att_cash\";s:4:\"0.00\";s:7:\"contact\";s:11:\"15021452141\";s:10:\"unique_num\";N;s:8:\"ext_time\";N;s:8:\"ext_desc\";N;s:10:\"task_union\";s:1:\"0\";s:12:\"alipay_trust\";N;s:8:\"is_del